extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
Game Night is an out-of-the-box introductory multiplayer Magic experience—a way for an engaged Magic player to introduce friends to the game, or for gaming groups to have their first Magic experience together. What Planeswalker Decks are to one-on-one, Game Night is to multiplayer.

Contents:
• 5 60-card decks
• 5 Spindown life counters
• 5 life counter platforms
• 20 +1/+1 counters
• 15 double-sided tokens
• 5 rules reference cards
• 1 rulebook
